Ayala Corp. Says It Will Redeem Early 6 Billion Peso Bonds

-- B y   C e c i l i a   Y a p
-- 
2011-09-28T07:07:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/ayala-corp-says-it-will-redeem-early-6-billion-peso-bonds.html
Ayala Corp. (AC)  said its executive
committee approved the early redemption of 6 billion pesos ($138
million) of bonds on Nov. 22.  The bonds will be redeemed in cash at 100 percent of the
issue price plus all accrued and unpaid interest based on a
coupon rate of 6.825 percent and an early redemption penalty of
0.5 percent, Ayala said in a disclosure to the stock exchange
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Cecilia Yap at 
 cyap19@bloomberg.net  